{
  "video_id": "H3YbZs-tu-I",
  "title": "The Case for Basic Income | Sebastian Johnson | TEDxMidAtlantic",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 28060.0,
      "end_time": 32320.0,
      "text": "So, raise your hand if you&#39;ve heard of the basic income before."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 32320.0,
      "end_time": 34240.0,
      "text": "OK, so a couple of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 34240.0,
      "end_time": 37160.0,
      "text": "Well, the idea behind the basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 37160.0,
      "end_time": 39440.0,
      "text": "is that each citizen will receive"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 39440.0,
      "end_time": 42160.0,
      "text": "enough no-strings-attached guaranteed money"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 42160.0,
      "end_time": 45040.0,
      "text": "to cover basic living expenses."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 45040.0,
      "end_time": 46640.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s an idea that has led"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 46640.0,
      "end_time": 51120.0,
      "text": "to some interesting political bedfellows, recently."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 51120.0,
      "end_time": 53780.0,
      "text": "So both former Labor leader, Andy Stern,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 53780.0,
      "end_time": 56127.0,
      "text": "and conservative intellectual, Charles Murray,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 56127.0,
      "end_time": 59840.0,
      "text": "have written books on the topic."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 59840.0,
      "end_time": 62459.0,
      "text": "Both the Cato Institute and the movement for Black Lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 62459.0,
      "end_time": 67160.0,
      "text": "have endorsed the basic income, though from very different perspectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 67160.0,
      "end_time": 69060.0,
      "text": "And just last week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 69060.0,
      "end_time": 71580.0,
      "text": "President Obama suggested that the basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 71580.0,
      "end_time": 73920.0,
      "text": "would be a part of our national conversation"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73920.0,
      "end_time": 76788.0,
      "text": "for the next two decades."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 76788.0,
      "end_time": 79320.0,
      "text": "Now, I know what you&#39;re thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 79320.0,
      "end_time": 80760.0,
      "text": "what are you doing on stage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 80760.0,
      "end_time": 83880.0,
      "text": "and why aren&#39;t any of those people here that you just mentioned?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83880.0,
      "end_time": 85400.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85400.0,
      "end_time": 88137.0,
      "text": "The short answer is that I said, &quot;Yes,&quot; and they didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88137.0,
      "end_time": 89457.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89457.0,
      "end_time": 90600.0,
      "text": "But the longer answer is"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90600.0,
      "end_time": 94800.0,
      "text": "that I&#39;m both a student and a beneficiary of public policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94800.0,
      "end_time": 99188.0,
      "text": "I believe that the public policy has the power to transform lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99188.0,
      "end_time": 100760.0,
      "text": "and I think that the basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 100760.0,
      "end_time": 104460.0,
      "text": "is one path forward to a more just future."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104460.0,
      "end_time": 106080.0,
      "text": "So this idea is a little different"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 106080.0,
      "end_time": 108270.0,
      "text": "from the others you&#39;ve heard at the conference,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 108270.0,
      "end_time": 110440.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s not a new idea at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 110440.0,
      "end_time": 113720.0,
      "text": "In fact, Thomas Paine first suggested a basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 113720.0,
      "end_time": 116160.0,
      "text": "as an economic right for every citizen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 116160.0,
      "end_time": 118680.0,
      "text": "in 1792."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118680.0,
      "end_time": 120560.0,
      "text": "In the 1960s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120560.0,
      "end_time": 122920.0,
      "text": "both Milton Friedman and Martin Luther King"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122920.0,
      "end_time": 126960.0,
      "text": "suggested a basic income to fight poverty here in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 126960.0,
      "end_time": 131010.0,
      "text": "And it almost became law in this country, under..."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 131009.99999999999,
      "end_time": 134527.0,
      "text": "Richard Nixon, of all people, in 1971."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134527.0,
      "end_time": 138080.0,
      "text": "So I can see that a couple of you in the audience are thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 138080.0,
      "end_time": 141487.0,
      "text": "&quot;Free money for everyone, that is un-American,&quot; right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141487.0,
      "end_time": 143530.0,
      "text": "You know, these people don&#39;t need a check."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143530.0,
      "end_time": 147200.0,
      "text": "They need to get a job, they need to make better choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147200.0,
      "end_time": 148840.0,
      "text": "And if we give everyone a handout,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 148840.0,
      "end_time": 151232.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s going to lead to a culture of dependency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 151232.0,
      "end_time": 155640.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s going to lead to laziness and vice."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 155640.0,
      "end_time": 158800.0,
      "text": "But social science research over the last couple of decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 158800.0,
      "end_time": 162845.0,
      "text": "have shown that many of the ideas we have about poverty and the poor"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 162845.0,
      "end_time": 165640.0,
      "text": "are dead wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 165640.0,
      "end_time": 167760.0,
      "text": "Poor choices don&#39;t lead to poverty:"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 167760.0,
      "end_time": 170504.0,
      "text": "in fact, poverty can limit choices"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 170504.0,
      "end_time": 174320.0,
      "text": "and lead to poor outcomes in surprising ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174320.0,
      "end_time": 178290.0,
      "text": "One study shows that the effect of poverty on your decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 178290.0,
      "end_time": 182320.0,
      "text": "about your finances and your health and your job"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182320.0,
      "end_time": 185931.0,
      "text": "is equivalent to 13 lost IQ points."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185931.0,
      "end_time": 188360.0,
      "text": "And the conditions that are associated with poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188360.0,
      "end_time": 192080.0,
      "text": "like violence, malnutrition, abuse, and pollution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192080.0,
      "end_time": 196600.0,
      "text": "can stunt brain development, particularly for young brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 196600.0,
      "end_time": 204720.0,
      "text": "And so poverty is the cause and not the effect of poor choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204720.0,
      "end_time": 208836.0,
      "text": "Programs that try to fight poverty by changing behavior won&#39;t work."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 208836.0,
      "end_time": 210360.0,
      "text": "In fact, it&#39;s just the opposite:"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 210360.0,
      "end_time": 213000.0,
      "text": "Cash transfers are one way"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 213000.0,
      "end_time": 217360.0,
      "text": "that we can expand choices and lead to better outcomes for families."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217360.0,
      "end_time": 220480.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll give you an example from my own family."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 220480.0,
      "end_time": 223573.0,
      "text": "My mother Denise was born here, in Washington DC."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223573.0,
      "end_time": 226066.0,
      "text": "She was the youngest of seven kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226066.0,
      "end_time": 227400.0,
      "text": "And my grandmother struggled"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227400.0,
      "end_time": 231960.0,
      "text": "to provide the basics on a postal worker salary."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231960.0,
      "end_time": 234080.0,
      "text": "And it was a cash transfer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234080.0,
      "end_time": 238055.0,
      "text": "an unexpected cash transfer in the form of social security survivor benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238055.0,
      "end_time": 240196.0,
      "text": "that allowed my mother to go to college."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 240196.0,
      "end_time": 242980.0,
      "text": "And she was the first person in our family to get a degree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 242980.0,
      "end_time": 245680.0,
      "text": "right here at the University of the District of Columbia."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245680.0,
      "end_time": 248520.0,
      "text": "And without that no-strings-attached cash transfer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 248520.0,
      "end_time": 253200.0,
      "text": "both her choices and my own would look a lot different today."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 253200.0,
      "end_time": 255080.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not just my own family:"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 255080.0,
      "end_time": 258040.0,
      "text": "There have been studies across decades, and in many countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 258040.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261279.00000000003,
      "text": "that show that the basic income does not discourage work."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 261279.0,
      "end_time": 263539.0,
      "text": "In fact it encourages entrepreneurship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 263539.0,
      "end_time": 266120.0,
      "text": "and allows people to continue their schooling."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 266120.0,
      "end_time": 270720.0,
      "text": "Recipients report better health outcomes, and better nutrition."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 270720.0,
      "end_time": 274990.0,
      "text": "And a randomized controlled trial conducted in Kenya and Uganda shows"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274990.0,
      "end_time": 278360.0,
      "text": "that there is no statistically significant increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 278360.0,
      "end_time": 280800.0,
      "text": "in alcohol or tobacco consumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 280800.0,
      "end_time": 283760.0,
      "text": "from a basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 283760.0,
      "end_time": 285880.0,
      "text": "So if the success of cash transfers"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 285880.0,
      "end_time": 289680.0,
      "text": "are one reason to support the basic income,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 289680.0,
      "end_time": 291301.0,
      "text": "another reason is that employment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291301.0,
      "end_time": 294680.0,
      "text": "you know, the idea that you just need to get a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 299800.0,
      "text": "that no longer is a guarantee to keep you out of poverty."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 299800.0,
      "end_time": 303864.0,
      "text": "A cash transfer allowed my mother to enter the middle class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 303864.0,
      "end_time": 305960.0,
      "text": "but it was her job as a public school teacher"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 305960.0,
      "end_time": 308200.0,
      "text": "that kept us in the middle class."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308200.0,
      "end_time": 310160.0,
      "text": "And the story of the last three decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 310160.0,
      "end_time": 313080.0,
      "text": "has been the slow disappearance of those jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 313080.0,
      "end_time": 316170.0,
      "text": "Jobs that provide retirement benefits,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316170.0,
      "end_time": 319460.0,
      "text": "paid time off,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 319460.0,
      "end_time": 326680.0,
      "text": "raises, periodically."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 326680.0,
      "end_time": 332660.0,
      "text": "In 1960, the three largest employers were GM, AT&amp;T, and Ford."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 332660.0,
      "end_time": 336680.0,
      "text": "Places that provided good union jobs."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 336680.0,
      "end_time": 341440.0,
      "text": "Today, three of the largest employers are Walmart, McDonalds and Yum! brands,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 341440.0,
      "end_time": 346714.0,
      "text": "places where workers struggle to make it past the poverty line."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 346714.0,
      "end_time": 348000.0,
      "text": "In Lawrence, Massachusetts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 348000.0,
      "end_time": 351760.0,
      "text": "is a former factory town where I taught elementary school."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351760.0,
      "end_time": 357480.0,
      "text": "The median family is $6,300 poorer than they were in 1980,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 357480.0,
      "end_time": 360659.0,
      "text": "largely because the jobs that have replaced factory jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 360659.0,
      "end_time": 365360.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t pay nearly as well or offer as many benefits."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 365360.0,
      "end_time": 370520.0,
      "text": "Now, more optimistic policymakers will say we&#39;ve heard this all before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 370520.0,
      "end_time": 372870.0,
      "text": "that in every previous era,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 372870.0,
      "end_time": 376020.0,
      "text": "new technology has led to more opportunities"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 376020.0,
      "end_time": 378765.0,
      "text": "than it has displaced or destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 378765.0,
      "end_time": 380480.0,
      "text": "And to a certain extent that&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 380480.0,
      "end_time": 387720.0,
      "text": "So if you are a Stagecoach driver, you could get a job driving a truck."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 387720.0,
      "end_time": 391540.0,
      "text": "But what about the horses?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 391540.0,
      "end_time": 393030.0,
      "text": "In 1900,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 393030.0,
      "end_time": 398200.0,
      "text": "there were over 21 million horses in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 398200.0,
      "end_time": 403080.0,
      "text": "By 1960, that number had dwindled to just over three million."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 403080.0,
      "end_time": 407280.0,
      "text": "Today, one Ford Focus can do the work of 160 horses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 407280.0,
      "end_time": 410112.0,
      "text": "and thanks to the computing revolution, we have machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 410112.0,
      "end_time": 413920.0,
      "text": "that can do the mental work of hundreds of human beings."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 413920.0,
      "end_time": 417520.0,
      "text": "Already there are algorithms that can outperform radiologists"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 417520.0,
      "end_time": 420480.0,
      "text": "in discovering cancerous tumors."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 420480.0,
      "end_time": 423130.0,
      "text": "The Associated Press uses software"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 423130.0,
      "end_time": 427169.0,
      "text": "to write 3,000 financial reports every quarter."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 427169.0,
      "end_time": 430600.0,
      "text": "Think of how many journalists that&#39;s displaced."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 430600.0,
      "end_time": 432840.0,
      "text": "One Oxford University study"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 432840.0,
      "end_time": 437640.0,
      "text": "found that 47 percent of Americans, nearly half of our workforce,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 437640.0,
      "end_time": 443577.0,
      "text": "is in danger of losing their job to a computer or a machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 443577.0,
      "end_time": 448000.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t simply retrain half of our workforce."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 448000.0,
      "end_time": 450760.0,
      "text": "We need a policy like the basic income"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 450760.0,
      "end_time": 455680.0,
      "text": "to provide the stability that employment once provided."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 455680.0,
      "end_time": 456912.0,
      "text": "Now we&#39;ve already seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 456912.0,
      "end_time": 461122.0,
      "text": "the effect of increasing disparities and increasing inequality"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 461122.0,
      "end_time": 464360.0,
      "text": "on our political and social system."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 464360.0,
      "end_time": 468351.0,
      "text": "Inequality is corrosive to democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 468351.0,
      "end_time": 469790.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t need to tell you that:"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 469790.0,
      "end_time": 472626.0,
      "text": "you can pick up a newspaper and look at any headline"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 472626.0,
      "end_time": 476100.0,
      "text": "and see that inequality is corrosive to democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476100.0,
      "end_time": 480160.0,
      "text": "And if we&#39;re serious about strengthening our social contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 480160.0,
      "end_time": 482840.0,
      "text": "and preparing ourselves for the next century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 482840.0,
      "end_time": 487000.0,
      "text": "we need a policy like the basic income."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 487000.0,
      "end_time": 492960.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s also not just inequality by race or class or gender;"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 492960.0,
      "end_time": 495040.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s inequality by place."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 495040.0,
      "end_time": 497400.0,
      "text": "So Washington is a prime example"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 497400.0,
      "end_time": 501022.0,
      "text": "of a city divided into haves and have-nots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 501022.0,
      "end_time": 503520.0,
      "text": "but this is a regional problem as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 503520.0,
      "end_time": 506720.0,
      "text": "One 2015 study of the 10 richest counties"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 506720.0,
      "end_time": 511520.0,
      "text": "found that five of the richest counties are here in the Washington DC area,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 511520.0,
      "end_time": 515679.0,
      "text": "and all but one are in the Northeast Corridor."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 515679.0,
      "end_time": 519320.0,
      "text": "Meanwhile, towns like Woonsocket, Rhode Island,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 519320.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521559.00000000006,
      "text": "which was hit hard by the recession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 521558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525360.0,
      "text": "that relies on its residents two million dollars in food stamp benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 525360.0,
      "end_time": 527927.0,
      "text": "just to power the local economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 527927.0,
      "end_time": 532400.0,
      "text": "those towns are left to wither in the shadows."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 532400.0,
      "end_time": 535200.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t concentrate our economy"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 535200.0,
      "end_time": 539160.0,
      "text": "in Washington, and in New York, and in Silicon Valley"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 539160.0,
      "end_time": 543080.0,
      "text": "and allow places like Woonsocket to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 543080.0,
      "end_time": 544714.0,
      "text": "We can no longer pretend"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 544714.0,
      "end_time": 547000.0,
      "text": "that the jobs of the past are going to come back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 547000.0,
      "end_time": 552080.0,
      "text": "or that employment will be enough to navigate an uncertain future."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 552080.0,
      "end_time": 556357.0,
      "text": "And we can&#39;t keep asking people to change their behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 556357.0,
      "end_time": 560400.0,
      "text": "instead of attending to their basic needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 560400.0,
      "end_time": 562490.0,
      "text": "Now is the time, more than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 562490.0,
      "end_time": 565760.0,
      "text": "to write new rules for our new economy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 565760.0,
      "end_time": 567560.0,
      "text": "as we did a century ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 567560.0,
      "end_time": 572440.0,
      "text": "when we decided that children belonged in schools and not in factories."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 572440.0,
      "end_time": 575878.0,
      "text": "When we decided that we could provide social security to our elders"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 575878.0,
      "end_time": 579960.0,
      "text": "as a part of our national birthright."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 579960.0,
      "end_time": 582293.0,
      "text": "When we determined that eight hours of honest work"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 582293.0,
      "end_time": 586289.0,
      "text": "should afford you the dignity of your dreams."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 586289.0,
      "end_time": 589880.0,
      "text": "I have faith that we will rise to the occasion."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 589880.0,
      "end_time": 591770.0,
      "text": "For while the ideas may be new,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 591770.0,
      "end_time": 594983.0,
      "text": "the spirit of our people endures."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 594983.0,
      "end_time": 596540.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 596540.0,
      "end_time": 606540.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}